  "body": "# Feature issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to have Dai as one of the **wallet currencies** ( = a currency you measure value in) so that, in the spirit of decentralization, people can use the wallet without seeing any fiat notions. This also helps cementing Dai as a world currency and getting people used to measuring value in Dai, which will be important when Dai will move away from the USD peg to something better.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n* displaying in Dai working just as in any other wallet currency\r\n* Dai here meaning Multi-Collateral Dai (MCD)\r\n* DAIUSD value actually pulled from an on-chain or off-chain source, not just a replacing of the USD symbol",
